   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Valerius, son of Heron. [[- - -]].;From volume three of the supplementary lists in the administration office of the strategos for the olive crop tax of the 22nd year. Keras, son of Aunes, grandson of Sambas, for a third part of one-half aroura of a date-palm grove: from the amounts deferred for the 22nd year, on account: 12 drachmai, and in the preceding deferment for the 23rd year, 7 drachmai, 1 obol, 2 chalkoi; equal according to the above, 19 drachmai, 1 obol, 2 chalkoi.</ab>
         </div>
